question4b.value:
Type of Account: the sample is referent to two types of account: one of change activist accounts and another of Christian accounts. The sample will be drawn from the first accounts that show up on twitter that meet all the requirements for selection. These are:
1. Change activist accounts have the words "activist" or "activism" in their biographies;
2. Christian accounts have the words "Christian" or "Catholic" in their biographies;
3. Change activist accounts will be checked to verify if the account refers to pro-change activism;
4. All accounts have to tweet in English;
5. All accounts must not only have pictures in their feeds;
6. Accounts of "common citizens" (i.e. non-influencers and non-organizations) must not be verified, represent an organization, or have more than a user (i.e. a couple's account; a group of students).

